  "general_provisions": "This bill amends statutory provisions related to state courts.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>allows the Judicial Council to establish a division in the district court;<hr><ltbullet>addresses resources for a division established by the Judicial Council;<hr><ltbullet>addresses the transfer of certain actions to a division of the district court;<hr><ltbullet>modifies the number of applicants certified by the Appellate Court Nominating Commission to the governor when there is more than one vacancy for an appellate court; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
